    "body" : "You&#39;ve configured your netbeans project to ensure your application would compile <i>and</i> run on a JDK8 (which is obsolete at this point). Hence that warning. The fix isn&#39;t to &#39;specify the bootstrap classpath&#39; (you should <i>not</i> do that). The fix is to set the project to JDK24."
