    "body" : "I don&#39;t know how to change the project to run on JDK24.  The only JDK I have on my computer it JDK-17 and the only &#39;8&#39; I can find in my projects is UTF-8.  NetBeans 24 has been re-installed and the setup process allowed the choice of JDK-17 as the the default JDK.   Still puzzled, but greatly appreciate your help."
